replyContent: Hi David, Please follow set by step. Delete the app. Go to your phone settings, scroll down and select apps, tap Google play Services, tap storage, clear cache. Go back to settings. Tap Google Play Store, storage, and clear data. Reboot your phone, then reinstall the app. Let me know if this resolves the issue! -Ashlyn
